# takeSmallest

- _takeSmallest(data, n)_

Answer the _n_ smallest elements of _data_, sorted in ascending order.

Take the two smallest numbers in a list:

```
>>> [1 3 5 4].takeSmallest(2)
[1 3]
```

Get the two smallest quantities in a list of Quantity objects:

```
>>> [1.grams 2.kilograms 2.milligrams]
>>> .takeSmallest(2)
[2.milligrams 1.grams]
```

